      "id": "mtg-gap-002",
      "question": "Is a HELOC the same as a second mortgage?",
      "answer": "A HELOC is one type of second mortgage because it sits behind the first mortgage in lien priority, but not every second mortgage is a HELOC. A closed-end home equity loan is another common type of second mortgage.",
