      "id": "mtg-gap-004",
      "question": "Is recasting the same thing as refinancing?",
      "answer": "No. A recast keeps the same mortgage and lowers the monthly payment after a principal reduction, while a refinance replaces the old mortgage with a new loan that can change the rate, term, and structure.",
