      "id": "mtg-gap-021",
      "question": "What is the difference between prepaid items and closing costs?",
      "answer": "Closing costs are the broader set of fees and charges connected to the loan and transaction, while prepaid items are amounts collected in advance for things like interest, taxes, insurance, or escrow setup. Both can affect how much cash you need at closing.",
